        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Windows 11 開始功能表加入廣告　測試期間未有收到太多反對</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/windows-11-start-menu-ads/software/windows-11/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=windows-11-start-menu-ads</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/windows-11-start-menu-ads/software/windows-11/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 12:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[廣告]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1233378</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 在幾星期之前開始測試在 Windows 11 的「開始」功能表中，加入 Microsoft Store 的廣告，而最近測試終於通過，陸續透過更新向所有用家提供。<br /><span id="more-1233378"></span></p><p>在 Windows 11 的更新説明中，Microsoft 表示「開始」功能表的「推薦」部分現在起會顯示一些 Microsoft Store 的 App 廣告，他們形容廣告中的 App 來自於小部分精心策劃的開發者，廣告本身旨在幫助 Windows 11 用户發現更多 App，但在很大程度上將使更多 Windows 應用的開發者受惠。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Looks like outright ads might be coming to the Start Menu in Windows 11, not just the usual recommendations / tips / shortcuts / etc.<br />After enabling experiment 48797684 the text in Settings changes slightly to accommodate for this 😐 <a href="https://t.co/BVEPe0nGgr">https://t.co/BVEPe0nGgr</a><a href="https://t.co/rTcG4rV8iR">pic.twitter.com/rTcG4rV8iR</a></p><p>&mdash; Albacore ☁️ (@thebookisclosed) <a href="https://twitter.com/thebookisclosed/status/1783104696493682903?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 24, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>在測試期間 Microsoft 主要是「試水温」看看社羣會否有很大的反對聲音，現在看來並沒有太多人反對，而其實這個「功能」是可以在設定中關閉，只需要在設定的「個人化」›「開始」中關閉顯示推薦項目的選項，廣告就會消失，但同時其他「推薦」的項目例如最近使用的文件也會一併不顯示。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.xda-developers.com/windows-11-start-menu-ads-avoid/">XDA developers</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/meta-ai-advantage/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Meta AI 廣告工具成效欠佳　廣告客户抱怨成本上升但效果參差</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/13/microsoft-starts-testing-ads-in-the-windows-11-start-menu/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Windows 11 測試在「開始」落廣告　為 Microsoft Store App 作宣傳</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/29/wordpad-will-be-removed-in-windows-11-version-24h2-microsoft-confirms/software/pc-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">在 Windows 預載近 30 年   Microsoft 確認 WordPad 將被移除</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/windows-11-start-menu-ads/software/windows-11/">Windows 11 開始功能表加入廣告　測試期間未有收到太多反對</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/windows-11-start-menu-ads/software/windows-11/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>保時捷第三代 Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 抵港，車身設計、車廂內部科技搶先睇</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/porsche-panamera-2024/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=porsche-panamera-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/porsche-panamera-2024/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 10:42:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Panamera]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[porsche]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Taycan]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1233377</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>保時捷第三代 Panamera 車系正式到香港，早前於全新開幕的香港保時捷旗艦陳列室舉行了傳媒發布會。小編都有代表 unwire 出席，以下就詳細同大家睇睇！</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1233402 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_145826-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1233401 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_153317-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0023.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Panamera 運動型豪華房車的領軍車款，已隆重進駐灣仔全新旗艦陳列室。保時捷 Panamera 升級至第三代車款，進一步提升 E-Hybrid 混合動力技術和高階主動式底盤控制系統。加入大量創新技術包括 Porsche Active Ride 懸掛系統，能夠結合運動駕駛模式與令人滿意的舒適度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0000.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233383" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>第三代保時捷 Panamera 擁有優雅的車身設計，外觀科技感十足。長度為 5,052 mm（行政加長版為 5,202 mm），寬度 1,937 mm，高度 1,423 mm（行政加長版為 1,428 mm）。重新設計的進氣口滿足了動力傳動系統的需求，車身線條和比例依舊保留車系的特色，側窗線條進一步強化四門跑車的特徵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233385" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>車廂內，Porsche Driver Experience 結合數碼化與實體觸控方式，所有操作介面及顯示概念以駕駛者為中心設計。Normal、Sport 和 Sport Plus 模式開關也在駕駛者可輕鬆觸及的範圍內，方便駕駛時快速切換。副駕乘客亦可利用 10.9 吋顯示屏幕查看性能數據或觀看影片與享受娛樂系統。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233388" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0014.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233389" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0016-rotated.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>中控台上 Panamera 結合保時捷通訊管理系統（PCM），駕駛者可將自己的線上帳户與車輛連接，並通過 Apple CarPlay 和 Android Auto 連接電話及車輛數據，提升便利性。MyPorsche 應用程序整合進 Apple CarPlay 中，進一步提升了可用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233386" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0009.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233387" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在科技方面，Panamera 標配 LED 矩陣光束大燈，提供更好的照明。可選的 HD-LED 矩陣光束大燈，照明範圍可達 600 公尺。輔助系統如 Porsche InnoDrive 與交通標誌辨識系統協同工作，實現主動道路引導。新車型還提供了遠端停車輔助功能，駕駛者可透過智能手機監控停車操作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233391" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0018.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240503_154827-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>駕駛安全系統包括突破性的底盤科技 Porsche Active Ride 懸掛系統，標配主動式雙閥門氣壓減震器，能獨立調整壓縮和回彈，減輕路面衝擊的同時提高動態駕駛的穩定性。E-Hybrid 車型更能選配這一懸吊系統，提供前所未有的平衡。</p><p>全新 E-Performance 技術為 E-Hybrid 車型提供更強性能和續航。Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 採用 4.0 公升雙渦輪增壓 V8 引擎搭配 140 kW 摩打，總輸出達 500 kW（680PS）、最高扭力為 930Nm，0-100 km/h 加速僅需 3.2 秒，最高車速可達 315km/h。Panamera 車款則搭載 2.9 公升 V6 雙渦輪增壓引擎，輸出功率達 260 kW (353PS)、峯值扭力 500Nm，並搭載重新設計的八速 PDK 變速箱，實現輕量化和更高持續輸出。基本款 Panamera 從靜止加速到 100 km/h 的時間縮短至 5.1 秒，並將最高車速提升至 272 km/h。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0019.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1233394" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/unwire0002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 Panamera 車系已登陸座落於灣仔核心地段的全新香港保時捷旗艦陳列室。</p><p>全新 <b>Panamera </b>現已接受訂購，售價為：</p><p>Panamera 港幣 $1,838,000 起</p><p>Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>$3,768,000 起</p><p><i>*</i>製造商建議零售價 (包括首次登記税)<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><h2>Panamera 規格</h2><p>動力：2.9 公升 V6 雙渦輪增壓引擎</p><p>輸出功率： 260 kW (353PS)</p><p>峯值扭力：500Nm</p><p>0-100km/h 加速時間：5.1 秒</p><p>最高車速：272 km/h</p><h2>Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 規格</h2><p>動力：4.0 公升雙渦輪增壓 V8 引擎搭配 140 kW 摩打</p><p>輸出功率：500 kW（680PS）</p><p>峯值扭力：930Nm</p><p>0-100 km/h 加速時間：3.2 秒</p><p>最高車速：315km/h</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/13/vehicles-getting-increasingly-problematic/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">J.D. Power 報告指電動車問題多　美國最可靠車款為 Porsche 718</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/08/taycan-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">保時捷純電跑車 Taycan 小改款，性能更強 + 續航力提升三成</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/04/porsche-panamera-2024/life-tech/auto/">保時捷第三代 Panamera Turbo E-Hybrid 抵港，車身設計、車廂內部科技搶先睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
